ators, it doesn't actually feature them.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/2019/12/6/20998648/2019-youtube-rewind-dislikes-2018 |title=2019 YouTube Rewind apologizes for 2018 Rewind, is still massively disliked |last=Radulovic |first=Petrana |date=2019-12-06 |website=Polygon |language=en |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206164626/https://www.polygon.com/2019/12/6/20998648/2019-youtube-rewind-dislikes-2018 |archive-date=December 6, 2019 |access-date=2019-12-06}}</ref> The video has also been criticized as being lazily made, as it's simply a mash-up of existing videos, and that the quality of 2019 does not stand up to the one in 2018 and that [[WatchMojo.com|WatchMojo]] looks to have made it\n\n;Appearances of YouTube personalities and special guests:\nNotable YouTube creators featured in the video include:<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web |url=https://rewind.youtube/about |title=YouTube Rewind 2019 |website=YouTube Rewind 2019 |language=en |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206003210/https://rewind.youtube/about/ |archive-date=December 6, 2019 |access-date=December 6, 2019}}</ref>\n\n1MILLION Dance Studio, A4, Anaysa, Andymation, [[Ariana Grande]], Awez Darbar, Azzyland, [[Billie Eilish]], Black Gryph0n, [[Blackpink|BLACKPINK]], ChapkisDanceUSA, [[Daddy Yankee]], [[David Dobrik]], [[Dude Perfect]], [[Felipe Neto]], Fischer\u2019s- \u30d5\u30a3\u30c3\u30b7\u30e3\u30fc\u30ba, [[Galen Hooks]], ibighit, [[James Charles (Internet personality)|James Charles]], [[Jeffree Star]], Jelly, [[Kylie Jenner]], [[LazarBeam]], [[Lil Dicky]], [[Lil Nas X]], LOUD, LOUD Babi, LOUD Coringa, Magnet World, [[MrBeast]], Nilson Izaias Papinho Oficial, [[Noah Schnapp]], \ubc31\uc885\uc6d0\uc758 \uc694\ub9ac\ube44\ucc45 Paik's Cuisine, Pencilmation, [[PewDiePie]], Seth Everman, [[Shane Dawson]], Team Naach, whinderssonnunes,\uc6cc\ud06c\ub9e8-Workman, \ud558\ub8e8\ud55c\ub07c one meal a day\n\nSongs in YouTube Rewind 2019:\n*\"[[7 