nce)|Flossing]], [[Will Smith]]'s [[Grand Canyon]] bungee jump, the [[In My Feelings#Release and reception|\"In My Feelings\" Challenge]], [[PewDiePie]] chair memes, [[Wedding of Prince Harry and Meghan Markle|the royal wedding of Prince Harry and Meghan Markle]], [[Autonomous sensory meridian response|ASMR]], Japanese Foil Ball Challenge, [[Mukbang|Mukbang Challenge]], melting lipsticks, [[2018 FIFA World Cup Group B|the match between Portugal and Spain in the 2018 FIFA World Cup]], Football Challenge, [[Elon Musk's Tesla Roadster]], [[Figure skating at the 2018 Winter Olympics \u2013 Team event|figure skating at the 2018 Winter Olympics]] and [[Mason Ramsey|the viral video by a boy in a Walmart store yodelling]]. The video also highly references the controversial online video game ''[[Fortnite]]''.\n\nThe video referenced popular music videos including, [[BTS (band)|BTS]]'s \"[[Idol (BTS song)|Idol]]\", [[Marshmello]] and [[Bastille (band)|Bastille]]'s \"[[Happier (Marshmello and Bastille song)|Happier]]\", [[Kanye West]] and [[Lil Pump]]'s \"[[I Love It (Kanye West and Lil Pump song)|I Love It]]\", [[Drake (musician)|Drake]]'s \"In My Feelings\", [[El Chombo]]'s \"[[Dame Tu Cosita]]\", and [[Pinkfong]]'s \"[[Baby Shark]]\".\n\nAs of December 13, 2018, Everyone Controls Rewind became the most disliked video on the platform,<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/digital/news/youtube-rewind-2018-most-disliked-video-ever-1203088810/ |title=YouTube Rewind 2018 Officially Becomes Most-Disliked Video Ever |last=Spangler |first=Todd  |date=2018-12-13 |website=Variety |language=en |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213183839/https://variety.com/2018/digital/news/youtube-rewind-2018-most-disliked-video-ever-1203088810/ |archive-date=December 13, 2018 |access-date=2019-04-27}}</ref> surpassing the previous holder of the title, \"[[Baby (Justin Bieber song)|Baby]]\" by [[Justin Bieber]]. Everyone Controls Rewind is also the first video to surpass ten million dislikes (December 2018), and 16 million dislikes (March 2019).\n\n;Appearances of YouTube personalities and special guests<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.portal-a.com/youtube-rewind-2018-everyone-controls-rewind/ |title=YouTube Rewind 2018: Everyone Controls Rewind {{!}} |website=www.portal-a.com |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209124131/https://www.portal-a.com/youtube-rewind-2018-everyone-controls-rewind/ |archive-date=December 9, 2018 |access-date=December 7, 2018}}</ref>\nNotable YouTube creators featured in the video include:<ref name=\"YTRewind2018Creators\">''Replaced'': {{Cite web |url=https://rewind.youtube/creators |title=Rewind 2018 {{!}} Creators |website=Rewind 2018 |language=en |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181208162124/https://rewind.youtube/creators |archive-date=December 8, 2018 |access-date=December 7, 2018}} \u2014 ''For'': {{Cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/youtube-rewind-video-2018-every-celebrity-spotted-2018-12|title='YouTube Rewind 2018' is officially the most disliked video in YouTube history \u2014 here's why|last=Smith|first=Dave|website=Business Insider|access-date=December 7, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191013095830/https://www.businessinsider.com/youtube-rewind-video-2018-every-celebrity-spotted-2018-12|archive-date=October 13, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><!-- BLUELINKED names only, please. -->\n\n10Ocupados, [[Adam Rippon]], Afros e Afins por N\u00e1taly Neri, Alisha Marie, Ami Rodriguez, [[Anwar Jibawi]], [[AsapSCIENCE]], AuthenticGames, [[BB ki Vines]], Bearhug, Bie the Ska, Bilingirl, [[Bhuvan Bam]], [[:ja:\u5409\u7530\u3061\u304b|Chika]], Bokyem TV, CajuTV, [[Casey Neistat]], [[Caspar Lee|Caspar]], Cherrygumms, Collins Key, [[:de:Dagi Bee|Dagi Bee]], Desimpedidos, Diva Depress\u00e3o, Dolan Twins, [[Dominic Panganiban|Domics]], Dotty TV, Elle Mills, [[Emma Chamberlain|emma chamberlain]], [[Enes Batur]], [[:fr:EnjoyPhoeni