>\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 10\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 10\n |Title           = [[YouTube Rewind 2019: For the Record]]{{anchor|YouTube Rewind 2019: For the Record}}\n |Aux2            = 5:36\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|12|5}}\n |Aux4            = 33.6\n |LineColor      = 13599F\n |ShortSummary    = On December 5, 2019, \"YouTube Rewind 2019: For the Record\" was uploaded to the \"YouTube\" YouTube channel. The video is a mash-up of the best videos and creators in certain categories, including \"most viewed\" and \"video games.\" The video starts off with creators reacting to the failure of YouTube Rewind 2018 followed by the text, \"In 2018, we made something you didn\u2019t like. For Rewind 2019, let\u2019s see what you DID like.\" Viewers have stated that although the video does show popular creators, it doesn't actually feature them.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/2019/12/6/20998648/2019-youtube-rewind-dislikes-2018 |title=2019 YouTube Rewind apologizes for 2018 Rewind, is still massively disliked |last=Radulovic |first=Petrana |date=2019-12-06 |website=Polygon |language=en |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206164626/https://www.polygon.com/2019/12/6/20998648/2019-youtube-rewind-dislikes-2018 |archive-date=December 6, 2019 |access-date=2019-12-06}}</ref> The video has also been criticized as being lazily made, as it's simply a mash-up of existing videos, and that the quality of 2019 does not stand up to the one in 2018 and that [[WatchMojo.com|WatchMojo]] looks to have made it\n\n;Appearances of YouTube personalities and special guests:\nNotable YouTube creators featured in the video include:<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web |url=https://rewind.youtube/about |title=YouTube Rewind 2019 |website=YouTube Rewind 2019 |language=en |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206003210/https://rewind.youtube/about/ |archive-date=December 6, 2019 |access-date=December 6, 2019}}</ref>\n\n1MILLION Da